widgets_values:
Unless your model is specifically lcm model, lcm lora is required:
https://huggingface.co/latent-consistency/lcm-lora-sdv1-5/blob/main/pytorch_lora_weights.safetensors
Use any lora you wish here
Use only generic style prompts here, and anything you want to exaggerate

Free increase to the sampling quality, often affects the colors negatively, I've adjusted the values a bit to compensate, not mandatory but most of the time it's an improvement. Costs no sampling time!
Negative prompt not going to affect anything at cfg 1.0, not important here.
This should be -2 for novel AI based models (most anime models for example), otherwise -1, check the model you use for recommendations

#Model links:
These are not set in stone, but I used these.
##Controlnets:
Pose:

https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/control_v11p_sd15_openpose/blob/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.fp16.safetensors

Depth:

https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/control_v11f1p_sd15_depth/blob/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.fp16.safetensors

Controlgif

https://huggingface.co/crishhh/animatediff_controlnet/blob/main/controlnet_checkpoint.ckpt

Tile

https://huggingface.co/lllyasviel/control_v11f1e_sd15_tile/blob/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.bin


##Model upscaler:
Ultra fast, tiny, works great with anime style especially:
https://openmodeldb.info/models/2x-Higurashi-v1-compact

##AnimateLCM:
https://huggingface.co/spaces/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/blob/main/models/Motion_Module/sd15_t2v_beta_motion.ckpt

LCM lora:

https://huggingface.co/latent-consistency/lcm-lora-sdv1-5/blob/main/pytorch_lora_weights.safetensors

##IPAdapter:
For IPAdapter you can use any, tho beware the plus models are too strong usually on rotating chars and such
Personal preference for most stuff:

https://huggingface.co/h94/IP-Adapter/resolve/main/models/ip-adapter_sd15_vit-G.safetensors

clip vision  CLIP-ViT-bigG-14-laion2B-39B-b160k:

https://huggingface.co/h94/IP-Adapter/resolve/main/sdxl_models/image_encoder/model.safetensors
Alternatively, load your own background style image here and connect it instead
